<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <title>Challenge #<%= challenge.id %> - Arena</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-dark text-light">
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

        <div class="container py-5">
            <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="mb-4">
                <ol class="breadcrumb">
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/" class="text-info text-decoration-none">Challenges</a></li>
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item active text-secondary" aria-current="page">Challenge #<%= challenge.id %>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </nav>

            <div class="row g-5">
                <!-- Left: Image and Instructions -->
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card bg-black border-secondary rounded-4 overflow-hidden mb-4">
                        <img src="/api/image/<%= challenge.result_image %>" class="img-fluid" alt="Challenge Image">
                    </div>
                    <div class="alert alert-info bg-dark border-info border-opacity-25 rounded-4 p-4">
                        <h4 class="h5 fw-bold text-info mb-3">어떻게 참여하나요?</h4>
                        <ol class="small text-secondary mb-0">
                            <li class="mb-2">위 이미지를 보고 어떤 프롬프트로 만들어졌을지 추측해보세요.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><a href="https://arena.ai" target="_blank"
                                    class="text-info fw-bold">arena.ai</a> 등에서 프롬프트를 테스트하고 이미지를 생성해보세요.</li>
                            <li>가장 유사하다고 생각되는 이미지와 프롬프트를 아래 폼에 제출하세요!</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right: Submission and Leaderboard -->
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <!-- Submission Form -->
                    <div class="card bg-black border-info border-opacity-25 rounded-4 p-4 shadow-lg mb-5">
                        <h2 class="h4 text-info mb-4 fw-bold">🚀 도전하기</h2>
                        <form id="submitForm">
                            <input type="hidden" id="challenge_id" value="<%= challenge.id %>">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label text-secondary small">닉네임</label>
                                <input id="name" type="text" class="form-control bg-dark text-white border-secondary"
                                    required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label text-secondary small">나의 결과 이미지</label>
                                <input id="image_file" type="file" accept="image/*"
                                    class="form-control bg-dark text-white border-secondary" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label text-secondary small">추측한 프롬프트 (10-100자)</label>
                                <textarea id="prompt" class="form-control bg-dark text-white border-secondary" rows="3"
                                    minlength="10" maxlength="100" placeholder="위 이미지를 생성했을 것으로 예상되는 프롬프트를 입력하세요."
                                    required></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" id="submitBtn"
                                class="btn btn-info btn-lg w-100 text-white fw-bold">채점하기</button>
                            <div id="status" class="mt-3 text-center small"></div>
                        </form>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Leaderboard -->
                    <div class="leaderboard-section">
                        <h3 class="h5 fw-bold text-info mb-4">🏆 RANKING</h3>
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table
                                class="table table-dark table-hover align-middle leaderboard-table border-secondary border-opacity-25">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr class="text-secondary small">
                                        <th>순위</th>
                                        <th>닉네임</th>
                                        <th>유사도</th>
                                        <th>일자</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <% if (leaderboard && leaderboard.length> 0) { %>
                                        <% leaderboard.forEach((r, i)=> { %>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td class="fw-bold text-warning">
                                                    <%= i + 1 %>
                                                </td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <span class="d-block text-white">
                                                        <%= r.name %>
                                                    </span>
                                                    <small class="text-secondary opacity-75">
                                                        <%= r.ip || "-" %>
                                                    </small>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="text-info fw-bold">
                                                    <%= r.prompt_score %>
                                                </td>
                                                <td class="text-secondary opacity-75">
                                                    <%= new Date(r.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <% }) %>
                                                <% } else { %>
                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td colspan="4" class="text-center py-3 text-secondary small">아직
                                                            도전자가 없습니다. 첫 번째 주인공이 되어보세요!</td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                    <% } %>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
            <script src="/script/form.js"></script>
</body>

</html>